codes.code: argmax 'This is a quiz of your ability to understand latin grammar. For each problem there is a ~ character in the text and your job is to figure out what word should be replaced by the ~. Provide the answer only. 1. Italia in Eurōpā ~. Choose from this set of possible answers [ est, est, sunt, est, est, est, sunt, est, sunt] [ANSWER]' from 'openai/text-davinci-002' where ANSWER in [ 'est', 'est', 'sunt', 'est', 'est', 'est', 'sunt', 'est', 'sunt']
